        "text": "=Classify this email into one of these categories: package_change, good_review, fault, or other.\n\nEmail Subject: {{ $json.headers.subject }}\nEmail From: {{ $json.from.text }}\nEmail Content: {{ $json.text }}\n\nSet the category field to exactly one of these values: package_change, good_review, fault, other",
