        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an email classification assistant. Analyze emails and categorize them accurately. Categories:\n- package_change: Emails about delivery changes, shipping updates, address modifications\n- good_review: Positive feedback, testimonials, satisfied customer reviews\n- fault: Complaints, issues, problems, negative feedback\n- other: Everything else"
